    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our game is a visual novel/scroller adventure telling the story of Toby. <br>Toby is a turtle who is well on in his years and has seen much. <br>He ventures out into the woods behind his home, where he and his wife always used to go on walks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our story focuses  on a complex topic: loss and grief. <br>It reminds us that not all journeys are the same; in some, you may only be able to lend an ear, and in some, you can help calm their worries. <br>But, regardless, you have to keep moving forward. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Toby continues, he will encounter multiple woodland creatures in the forest. Each character, along the way, represents a different stage of grief. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you talk with them, you collect a flower from each one. You will learn more about their dilemmas while also learning about Toby's mental journey.</p>",
